          "settings": {
            "content_heading": "Why You'll Love Our Napkins",
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>Artisanal Charm: </strong>Each napkin is hand block-printed, making every piece unique and full of character.</li><li><strong>Soft & Durable: </strong>Crafted from high-quality cotton that feels gentle on your hands and stands up to daily use.</li><li><strong>Versatile Elegance:</strong> Perfect for casual meals, festive dinners, weddings, or gifting to loved ones.</li><li><strong>Eco-Friendly & Sustainable: </strong>Reusable napkins made with natural dyes help you reduce waste without sacrificing style.</li><li><strong>Timeless Design:</strong> Intricate border prints bring a sophisticated, handcrafted touch to any table setting.</li><li><strong>Coordinated Table Styling: </strong>Pairs beautifully with tablecloths, placemats, and runners for a complete look.</li><li><strong>Vibrant, Fade-Resistant Prints: </strong>Traditional block printing ensures rich colors that last wash after wash.</li></ul>",
